Title: S5 Ep. 194 John Crossman
Description:
One of the most interesting people you can listen to because he is engaged and giving back in the Central Florida community. Multiple industries - Real estate, Education, Career Development, Nonprofit.  His thoughts about what 2030 jobs and industries will look like are interesting. 

Tune in and listen why he enjoys giving back and his birthday is May 11. Be sure to tell him happy birthday and ask about his mom's book.
